'''Magic publications''' are [[books]] and [[periodicals]] which are created in support of the professional [[magic (illusion)|magician]] industry. They include reviews of new equipment and techniques, announcements of upcoming events, interviews with prominent magicians, announcements of awards, and columns on such subjects as the history and ethics of the art of magic. Most also feature various explanations and ideas pertaining to magic tricks/effects. Additionally you can commonly advertise for businesses and events with little charge.
